data.description: Here is the ONE you have been waiting for! This beautiful country home has it all with 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, an Office (could be 5th bedroom), and Shop all on an acre of land. This home has lots of updates and features such as new flooring, paint, fixtures, newer AC, fireplace, double oven in kitchen, a safe room in master closet and beautiful landscaping with sprinkler system. The 30x30 shop features RV hookups, 220 outlet, additional parking off the side and a dogrun behind it. Call today for a private showing and make this beautiful property your home!
